item.title: Contributing
item.description: Your contribution is more than welcome. I have a Question/Problem If you have questions about how to use Laradock, please direct your questions to the discussion on Gitter. If you believe your question could help others, then consider opening an Issue (it will be labeled as Question) And you can still seek help on Gitter for it. I found an Issue If have an issue or you found a typo in the documentation, you can help us by opnening an Issue.
